{"tid":2120473,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"唔洗下載落部電話度，馬斯克親口證實：Neuralink 可將音樂直接串流到大腦","createTime":"2020-07-22T17:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T08:12:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4e9784f5fb65e227dff3d2ac0c72b923377def","tid":2120473,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/22100841/Image-22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F22100841%2FImage-22.jpg&h=cb935d40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉（Tesla）執行長馬斯克（Elon Musk）聲稱，他的植入式電腦介面 Neuralink 未來能將音樂直接串流到人類的大腦。發送想招聘腦機介面相關專案工程師的推文後，馬斯克在 Twitter 與另一位使用者交流時討論了這項技術。 <br />\n<br />\n「如果你已解決手機／穿戴式裝置的難題（密封、訊號處理、感應式充電、電源管理等），請考慮透過 engineering@neuralink.com 來我們這裡工作，」馬斯克 17 日推文表示：「解決大量、高可靠性、低成本的生產問題尤其重要。」<br />\n<br />\n2019 年直播展示時，馬斯克表示，Neuralink 會在大腦植入柔性電極導線，接收神經元（Neuron）訊號，然後再將訊號無線傳輸到鄰近的電腦。他指出，過程與 LASIK（Laser Epithelial Keratomileusis）手術很類似，雷射會在顱骨穿出一個小孔植入電極。<br />\n<br />\nNeuralink 技術有助於治療腦部病變，並透過荷爾蒙濃度控制提升身心能力<br />\n馬斯克認為，這項技術最終有助於治療阿茲海默症（Alzheimer&rsquo;s）、帕金森氏症（Parkinson&rsquo;s）和失智症（Dementia）等腦部病變。他補充，這對 AI 人工智慧與人類的共生（Symbosis）也至關重要。<br />\n<br />\n18 日馬斯克在 Twitter 回答許多使用者的其他問題，使用者問他 Neuralink 能否「幫助控制荷爾蒙濃度，並提升我們的優勢」（如增強生理機能和推理能力，抑或減輕焦慮等），「在需要時，可對強迫症（OCD）患者，停止神經網路的快速放電」，以及「有必要時，刺激催產素（Oxytocin）、血清素（Serotonin）和其他化學物質的釋放」。對每個問題，他都以簡單的「是」回答。<br />\n<br />\n今年 5 月，馬斯克在 Joe Rogan Experience Podcast 節目表示，他認為 Neuralink 專案有望一年內實現。7 月稍早，他也推文表示，將在 8 月 28 日公布 Neuralink 研究進展的更多訊息。需特別提醒的是，也很司空見慣，馬斯克經常會發表許多沒有任何實質意義的大膽主張與論述。"},{"pid":"60b29b7fc3ff16265b386113220cc198ff5bad15","tid":2120473,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:05:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cdn.technews.tw/2020/07/22/elon-musk-says-neuralink-will-stream-music-straight-into-your-brain/?utm_source=fb_tn&amp;utm_medium=facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.technews.tw%2F2020%2F07%2F22%2Felon-musk-says-neuralink-will-stream-music-straight-into-your-brain%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfb_tn%26utm_medium%3Dfacebook&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgIbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=580e1254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.technews.tw/2020/07/22/elon-musk-says-neuralink-will-stream-music-straight-into-your-brain/?utm_source=fb_tn&amp;utm_medium=facebook</a>"},{"pid":"b344cf8b68c5998f8a0ee3c4d10636f6e9d881ee","tid":2120473,"uid":235174,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:06:26.000Z","msg":"唔好亂黎呀，救救孩子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8433ed3f129bd950e4d79baa1917897cf6b6b9c9","tid":2120473,"uid":4574,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:07:10.000Z","msg":"仲顛過馬克思"},{"pid":"2dc896c5af5e5cb04b38e90170cfa08ca28ec98c","tid":2120473,"uid":11916,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:08:03.000Z","msg":"黑鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84681654c13568ababce3c74bb6604c6fa9a605","tid":2120473,"uid":1130,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:11:57.000Z","msg":"唔知點解睇完個topic個頭好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a3d8dcb20e0c495159384eeabeef50a4af6b2f","tid":2120473,"uid":63154,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:14:14.000Z","msg":"Google：正喎！不停串流廣告去啲人個腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b96043d3871754a9b977fb47be6e1cecde1f19b","tid":2120473,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:18:00.000Z","msg":"會唔會抽離唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2